&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://github.com/flutter/flutter/issues/157693" class="external-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&lt;img alt="Flutter ImageFilter.blur Issue" src="https://tech-andgar.me/posts/solving-artifacts-imagefilter-blur-flutter/images/preview-issue.webp">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="introducción">
 Introducción
 &lt;a class="heading-link" href="#introducci%c3%b3n">
